Dialogue:  0,0:00:08.90,0:00:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个对抗W.O.R.M的少女们的故事
Dialogue:  0,0:00:19.17,0:00:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钓鱼白痴瑛花姐
Dialogue:  0,0:00:22.45,0:00:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天翔少女真饵钓鱼记
Dialogue:  0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤静特别推荐
Dialogue:  0,0:00:28.87,0:00:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海边决战！钓斑鲅鱼！
Dialogue:  0,0:00:32.91,0:00:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四面被大海环抱的岛国日本
Dialogue:  0,0:00:36.70,0:00:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最被大众喜爱的钓法  果然还应该是海钓
Dialogue:  0,0:00:43.17,0:00:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海钓中  以区域的大小和咬钩时拉拽的力量来说
Dialogue:  0,0:00:49.32,0:00:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最为吸引人气的  还是钓斑鲅鱼
Dialogue:  0,0:00:54.75,0:00:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在钓斑鲅鱼的方法中  最为常见的钓法
Dialogue:  0,0:00:59.02,0:01:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用无机饵吸引鱼群  然后用浮钓法将鱼钓上来
Dialogue:  0,0:01:12.10,0:01:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以吧
Dialogue:  0,0:01:13.88,0:01:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑛花姐
Dialogue:  0,0:01:17.95,0:01:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好吧  瑛花姐  做这种事
Dialogue:  0,0:01:24.60,0:01:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有干劲啊
Dialogue:  0,0:01:26.46,0:01:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了啊  为什么
Dialogue:  0,0:01:31.49,0:01:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue:  0,0:01:34.45,0:01:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道还没有克服活饵恐惧症吗
Dialogue:  0,0:01:37.50,0:01:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那还怎么海钓啊
Dialogue:  0,0:01:41.54,0:01:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼章鱼什么的不用活饵也能钓到
Dialogue:  0,0:01:50.94,0:01:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  一条
Dialogue:  0,0:01:52.17,0:01:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue:  0,0:01:54.82,0:01:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不战而退了吗
Dialogue:  0,0:01:59.78,0:02:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue:  0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼饵的话  我会再帮你系的
Dialogue:  0,0:02:08.58,0:02:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了
Dialogue:  0,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来给你系
Dialogue:  0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个问题
Dialogue:  0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…是什么问题？
Dialogue:  0,0:02:21.55,0:02:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue:  0,0:02:25.80,0:02:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue:  0,0:02:27.10,0:02:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue:  0,0:02:29.84,0:02:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼
Dialogue:  0,0:02:31.08,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼
Dialogue:  0,0:02:32.47,0:02:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼
Dialogue:  0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼王啊！
Dialogue:  0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑛花姐  挂住了
Dialogue:  0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话好好看着
Dialogue:  0,0:02:56.74,0:02:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue:  0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了  Baby
Dialogue:  0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就是这么打算的吗
Dialogue:  0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue:  0,0:03:19.41,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼一被遮住眼睛  就会变老实呢
Dialogue:  0,0:03:23.94,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从书里读到的
Dialogue:  0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软软的
Dialogue:  0,0:03:29.62,0:03:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软软的…
Dialogue:  0,0:03:29.58,0:03:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…可怜
Dialogue:  0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从刚才开始就  在拿着什么呢
Dialogue:  0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是海牛
Dialogue:  0,0:03:36.11,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是属于腹足纲后鳃亚纲的软体动物
Dialogue:  0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue:  0,0:03:41.73,0:03:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软软的…
Dialogue:  0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又为什么要拿着那东西啊
Dialogue:  0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱不是吗
Dialogue:  0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗  海牛
Dialogue:  0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乌贼章鱼一样  都是软体动物哦
Dialogue:  0,0:04:05.26,0:04:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来要挑战世界上所有的虫子们
Dialogue:  0,0:04:13.78,0:04:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  瑛花
Dialogue:  0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要输啊  瑛花
Dialogue:  0,0:04:16.68,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之钓鱼白痴少女瑛花的战斗还在继续
Dialogue:  0,0:04:20.77,0:04:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喂
Dialogue:  0,0:04:22.69,0:04:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管海牛  要是不把活饵系上的话
Dialogue:  0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
